    tw-shadow-none
    tw-top-1

    tw-transform

    tw-absolute
    tw-w-full
    md:tw-w-5/5
    lg:tw-w-4/5

  :arrow="true"

  :items-to-show="itemsToShow"

  :has-grayscale="false"

>

      :team-selected="teamSelected"
      :screen-break-point="screenBreakPoint"
    />
